Package edu.ncsu.csc216.stp.model.test_plans

Class AbstractTestPlan

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.ncsu.csc216.stp.model.test_plans.AbstractTestPlan
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    FailingTestList, TestPlan
    public abstract class AbstractTestPlan
extends java.lang.Object
    AbstractTestPlan class is an abstract class at the top of the hierarchy for test plans. The AbstractTestPlan knows its testPlanName and the ISwapList of TestCases
    Author:
    Veerendra Gottiveeti, Yi Zhang
